snippet.title: Save One More trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist it on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/820240

Save One More is a heal'em up about the war where you are going to save lives instead of taking them.

Made by Stas Shostak https://www.shostak.games/
Music by Ira Lobanok https://www.facebook.com/ira.lobanok
3D models by Sergey Mozharovskiy https://twitter.com/S_Mozharovskiy
